name: CritterKin - Puppy Train Your Kids!
blurb: CritterKin - The App That Puppy Trains Your Kids

rewards.reward: WOOF: A BIG, slobbery Virtual Lick of Gratitude from the CritterKin Pups:  Thank you! We couldn\u2019t do this without you.

THE RAWHIDE CHEW: \r\nA personal email from CritterKin instructor Ms. Jenaia (aka Jena Ball) telling the story of the CritterKin pack for the FIRST time PLUS you'll receive a CritterKin Screensaver of the characters.

KIBBLE and BITS: A copy of the CritterKin app...PLUS a personalized thank you e-mail from both Martin Keltz (Emmy award winning producer of "The Magic School Bus") and Ms. Jenaia...PLUS the special CritterKin Screensaver...PLUS the CritterKin Slideshow featuring all the CritterKin characters...PLUS your name listed on the "CritterKin Founders Wall" on our Website.

BELLY RUBS (FOR EVERYONE): One copy of the CritterKin app....PLUS a personalized letter of thanks from the Emmy award winning producer of \u201cThe Magic School Bus,\u201d Martin Keltz on CritterKin stationery (delivered as a printable PDF)....PLUS a commemorative silicone bracelet inscribed with the words, \u201cI\u2019m a CritterKin Kickstarter\u201d....PLUS \u201cCritterKin Wearable Art\u201d Version I [Consists of a CritterKin dog tag (for humans) inscribed with the CritterKin logo and the message, \u201cLove Me, love My Dog\u201d].
